<br>
I think people tend to over state monk damage. It really isn't as good as people make it out to be. I have a large number of monk friends in game. They parse often, and even my uber friend says his dps is around 130dps max without disc. I can out do that with ease. I have suspend menion 2 now, and I am positive that once I get HoE, and max it, get FoM2 and 3..I will be able to sustain 190+ dps in a experience group. I was doing 145 before I got suspend menion. Now mana is a non-issue, and I can nuke freely baring aggro. A monk nor can a rogue hold a candle to me offensively. Mages are just to good now. Compare a mage with equal aa to any melee class in the game, and they will not be out damaged.<br>
<br>
Wezloc<br>
